condition.narrative: Annual Progress Review of Project Implementation

title.narrative: Number of firms receiving technical assistance from the Enterprise Support Services Fund (ESSF) reaches 200 by project end
500 long term jobs created through firms supported by ESSF business development services by project end.

actual.value: ESSF Fund is still being established. established, STEP support has increased micro enterprise turnover by 78.82%.

comment.narrative: Accuracy of STEP data to be verified at July implementation support mission.

title.narrative: Eliminate export taxes on artisanal products in 2010 from 10 % to 0 %
8. Number of tourists increased by 50% from 100,000 to 150,000 by project end
Teledensity (lines and cellular) increased from 2.5% to 30% by project end
Number of businesses registered annually at the one stop shop (Guichet Unique) increases by 50% by project end (number of companies)

actual.value: 1051 new businesses registered in 2009. New: Guichet Unique opened in May 2009.

comment.narrative: Accuracy to be verified during July implementation support mission.

title.narrative: Time taken to approve a new investment is reduced from 45 to 15 days by project end.
The cost of import-export licenses for artisanal products is reduced from 565,000 FCFA 10,000 FCFA by project end

actual.value: Exporting new and old artisanal projects are not subject to a license.

title.narrative: BHM (the Habitat Bank of Mali) has adopted and implemented a restructuring strategy by project end
Site and services provided for 5 ha by project end

comment.narrative: Investments cannot start before an adequate regulatory framework on industrial zones is in place

title.narrative: Zone's regulatory framework promulgated and implemented by project end.

comment.narrative: Studies and consultations by FIAS all completed.

title.narrative: Investment in the mining sector increased by 10% from US$ 155,000,000 to US$170,000,000 (approximately 5 new permits a year) by project end
Bank credit to SMEs increased to 30% of total loans and advances by project end.

comment.narrative: Accuracy to be verified during July 2010 implementation support mission.

title.narrative: Production from small and artisanal mines increased by 10% by project end (tones)
